-- Optional - Reflect "area of responsibbility" rather than physical work location

-- Regions can be rolled up into Region Hierarchies, often used to track geographic or sales region

-- Often used to facilitate "financial" reporting, can be used to attribute cost or revenue separately from where it originated
    - For eg: A worker in a US location who supports the UK office can have thier costs tagged to a UK region

-- Generaly not used HCM-only purposes
